              <p>Your age is just one of 10+ factors. Use the free CRS Calculator to see your complete score across all sections and find your fastest pathway to Canada PR.</p>
              <a href="https://crsscorecalculator.vercel.app/" class="btn btn-white">Full CRS Calculator →</a>
